of 23%. CONCLUSIONS: The evidence shows that ABPM is
cost-effective, avoiding iatrogenic effects and reducing
expenditure on treatment (grade of recommendation B). The
included studies provide a solid basis, but further evidence of
reproducibility is needed in research that is not based mainly on
analytical models.},
