medication-related adverse events, fatal and nonfatal
cardiovascular disease events, and noncardiovascular disease
death in LABBPS participants. Program costs, total direct health
care costs (2019 US dollars), and quality-adjusted life-years
(QALYs) were estimated for the LABBPS intervention and control
